        "text_PJxJEe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>You received the Three of Wands because your life is in a state of expansion, even if results aren’t fully visible yet. This card comes to people who have outgrown their current boundaries and are beginning to sense wider possibilities ahead.<\/h3><h3>You may feel a quiet impatience, a pull toward something larger, or a sense that staying still would be more uncomfortable than stepping forward. At the same time, you might not have all the information or certainty you want. <\/h3><h3>This card is here to tell you that this is alright. It is for those who want to think long-term rather than chase immediate validation. You are being asked to widen your perspective and honour the pace of your growth. It could be frustrating, but your acceptance of your circumstance matters. <\/h3><h3>Your future is opening up, and you will learn how to meet yourself without abandoning the present. Be confident, and trust the process. <br\/><br\/>On Love<\/h3><p>Relationships benefit from shared vision. Even if there is longer distance, proper planning and aligning goals will deepen your bond more than anything else. <\/p><h3>On Health<\/h3><p>Your energy will build gradually. You must practice consistency rather than function through bursts of effort. <\/p><h3>On Money \/ Career<\/h3><p>You could encounter novelty via countries, collaborations, opportunities, or markets. This is a year of planning your future success. <\/p><h3>How to work with this energy<\/h3><p>Think long-term and say yes to things even if they scare you. Just prepare carefully!<\/p><h3>Recommended products<\/h3><ol><li>Sunday Rituals Hair Repair & Growth Oil – Strengthening before growth<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Orange Grove Bag Charm (Orange) – Optimism & momentum<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Cross Braided Essentials Handbag – Green Mountains Edition – Vitality<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Enamel pin (Ranunculus) – Deep love <br\/><\/li><\/ol><p><br\/>You can find these in our pop-up booth at Night At Orchard, along the outdoor pathway between Ngee Ann City & Ion Orchard between 26-28 Dec, 3pm onwards <\/p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
